Source
------
BusyBox source (the basis of the binary distributed here):
  https://busybox.net/                  (upstream BusyBox)
  https://frippery.org/busybox/         (busybox-w32 Windows port)

Per GPLv2, the complete corresponding source for this binary is available from
the URLs above. Distributing this binary with the daemon obliges us to make that
source available to recipients; the upstream URLs satisfy that obligation.

The embedding (go:embed, extraction, PATH wiring) is the only modification on our
side; the busybox binary itself is unmodified upstream busybox-w32.
